rows.label: qst003102_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh? Are you all here to
help with distribution?

rows.label: qst003102_msg0002
rows.name: That would be a great help.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0003
rows.name:
This distribution center is short
on dishes made with vegetables...

rows.label: qst003102_msg0004
rows.name:
It would be a great help if you
could provide us with some.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0006
rows.name: Thank you for your hard work.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0007
rows.name:
Thanks to all of you, this
place should be fine now.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0009
rows.name:
We were never this busy before
the Acedian refugees arrived.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0010
rows.name:
That said, I believe now is the
time we should all be cooperating.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0011
rows.name:
Our current situation is
certainly very difficult.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0012
rows.name:
But with Acedia destroyed,
they have no choice but to
continue living here.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0013
rows.name:
Eventually, they will work and live
as citizens of this place, too.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0014
rows.name:
In that case, we cannot
treat them poorly.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0015
rows.name:
In any case, thank you. Thanks
to you, I think we have a little
more breathing room now.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0016
rows.name:
We need more vegetable dishes.
We're counting on you.
